59
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:27,800
OK.

60
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,480
Take her.

61
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,830
Yes. Let's go.

62
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,430
How are you? Are you OK?

63
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,160
Put me down.

64
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,390
Be quiet, I'm trying to save you.

65
00:06:17,390 --> 00:06:19,070
Sir, have mercy.

66
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:19,870
You're so handsome.

67
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,510
