72
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:30,720
Enough, shut up.

73
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:32,310
Unless you want to be taken by them.

74
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:33,070
Let's go.

75
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,830
Over there! Let's go!

76
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:41,680
Hurry!

77
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,480
Hurry up!

78
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,040
I misunderstood.

79
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,480
He was actually saving me.

80
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:08,120
It seems he's a good person.

81
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,750
Why did it start raining suddenly?

82
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,870
And so heavily.

83
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,680
Today,

84
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,430
thank you for saving me.

85
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,800
Who are you really?

86
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,190
Can you tell me?

87
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,390
Why were those people
trying to kidnap you?

88
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,560
I am...

89
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,560
Who am I?

90
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,950
I can't remember.

91
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,750
I... Who am I?

92
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,070
I can't remember.

93
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,830
Could it be that car accident?

94
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,630
You lost your memory?

95
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,680
Don't worry, take your time.

96
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,630
I can't remember...

97
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:10,120
I can't remember anything now.

98
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:12,510
You won't just leave me, will you?

99
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,070
From what you said,

100
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,560
