101
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:19,070
Cling sounds so unpleasant.

102
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:22,160
Let's call it helping instead.

103
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,870
You want me to help you?

104
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,680
You need to offer something in return.

105
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,160
Wait,

106
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,200
