are you?

107
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,440
Try to remember quickly.

108
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:34,790
I have things to ask you.

109
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:37,750
Until then, I'll help you.

110
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,030
None of you

111
