113
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,240
He's very skilled.

114
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,550
Clean up the scene and keep searching.

115
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:08,840
Keep searching!

116
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:09,840
